From: Sama Engine <engine@local>
Subject: [PATCH] renderer_vk: prefer MAILBOX over FIFO when vsync requested

Context
-------
bgfx's findPresentMode walks s_presentMode in order, picking the first
mode whose vsync flag matches the requested setting.  With the original
table, VK_PRESENT_MODE_FIFO_KHR is at index [0] with vsync=true, so it
is always picked when BGFX_RESET_VSYNC is set.  VK_PRESENT_MODE_MAILBOX_KHR
sits at index [2] with vsync=true but is never reached.

FIFO blocks vkAcquireNextImageKHR until SurfaceFlinger releases an image
back to the swapchain, which on Android happens at panel refresh — ~16.67
ms at 60 Hz.  This wait charges to the render thread (call site
SwapChainVK::acquire), fills bgfx's command ring, and back-pressures the
game thread's bgfx::frame() handoff, capping per-frame wall-clock at the
vsync period regardless of GPU work.

MAILBOX allows the render thread to keep submitting frames; the
compositor takes the most recent one at refresh and discards earlier
unpresented ones.  No tearing (still synchronized at refresh), no
acquire blocking when the swapchain has free images.

The cure
--------
Reorder s_presentMode so MAILBOX is checked before FIFO.  findPresentMode
will now pick MAILBOX when (a) BGFX_RESET_VSYNC is requested AND (b) the
device reports MAILBOX support; falls through to FIFO otherwise.

Also adds a BX_TRACE printing the selected mode so the integrating team
can verify the patch took effect via logcat (the bgfx callback we wire
up in engine/rendering/Renderer.cpp routes BX_TRACE to the
SamaEngineBgfx tag on Android).

Decision documented in docs/NOTES.md "Follow-up (2026-06-18, present
mode investigation)".

---
 bgfx/src/renderer_vk.cpp | 5 ++++-
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/bgfx/src/renderer_vk.cpp b/bgfx/src/renderer_vk.cpp
--- a/bgfx/src/renderer_vk.cpp
+++ b/bgfx/src/renderer_vk.cpp
@@ -150,9 +150,9 @@ VK_IMPORT_DEVICE

 	static const PresentMode s_presentMode[] =
 	{
+		{ VK_PRESENT_MODE_MAILBOX_KHR,      true,  "VK_PRESENT_MODE_MAILBOX_KHR"      },
 		{ VK_PRESENT_MODE_FIFO_KHR,         true,  "VK_PRESENT_MODE_FIFO_KHR"         },
 		{ VK_PRESENT_MODE_FIFO_RELAXED_KHR, true,  "VK_PRESENT_MODE_FIFO_RELAXED_KHR" },
-		{ VK_PRESENT_MODE_MAILBOX_KHR,      true,  "VK_PRESENT_MODE_MAILBOX_KHR"      },
 		{ VK_PRESENT_MODE_IMMEDIATE_KHR,    false, "VK_PRESENT_MODE_IMMEDIATE_KHR"    },
 	};

@@ -8160,6 +8160,9 @@ VK_IMPORT_DEVICE
 			BX_TRACE("Present mode not found! Defaulting to %s.", s_presentMode[idx].name);
 		}

+		BX_TRACE("Selected present mode: %s (vsync requested: %d)",
+			s_presentMode[idx].name, _vsync);
+
 		return idx;
 	}

